【解題方向】

第一想法：對於每一個 s[i] 都遍歷一次找最近的 c，Time Complexity 為 O(n^2) 

第二想法：先遍歷一遍 s 找到所有的 c，然後從所有的 c 開始向兩邊走
	=> 不過想到如何記錄狀態就覺得太複雜，而且可能最糟情況還是 Time Complexity 為 O(n^2) 

第三想法：看了提示，想到正向遍歷、反向遍歷一次，記錄 s[i] 與左右兩邊的 c 的最小距離
	=> 由於題目保證至少有一個 s 中至少有一個 c，對於每個 s[i]，其左或右必然會有一個 c

【程式碼】
```
// Time Complexity: O(n), n = s.length;
// Space Complexity: O(n), n = s.length;

/**
 * @param {string} s
 * @param {character} c
 * @return {number[]}
 */
var shortestToChar = function(s, c) {
    const chars = s.split('');
    const res = new Array(chars.length).fill(Infinity);

    let leftTargetCharIndex = -1;
    for (let i = 0; i < chars.length; i += 1) {
        if (chars[i] === c) leftTargetCharIndex = i;
        if (leftTargetCharIndex > -1) {
            res[i] = Math.min(res[i], Math.abs(leftTargetCharIndex - i));
        }
    }

    let rightTargetCharIndex = -1;
    for (let i = chars.length - 1; i > -1; i -= 1) {
        if (chars[i] === c) rightTargetCharIndex = i;
        if (rightTargetCharIndex > -1) {
            res[i] = Math.min(res[i], Math.abs(rightTargetCharIndex - i));
        }
    }

    return res;
};
```

1. 第一個直覺是用 recursion 來解題，不過過程中會遇到很多 edge case 沒有考慮到而 error thrown
2. 後來改用 stack 來實踐，也很清楚，不過需要搞懂什麼應該被放進 stack，以及 pop and push 的時機

```
// Time Complexity: O(n)
// Space Complexity: O(n)

/**
 * Recursive version of decodeString
 * @param {string} s
 * @return {string}
 */
var decodeString = function(s) {
    const helper = (str, index) => {
        let result = '';
        let num = 0;

        while (index < str.length) {
            const char = str[index];

            if (char >= '0' && char <= '9') {
                num = num * 10 + parseInt(char);
                index++;
            } else if (char === '[') {
                // Recursively decode the content inside brackets
                const [decodedStr, newIndex] = helper(str, index + 1);
                result += decodedStr.repeat(num);
                num = 0; // Reset number after using it
                index = newIndex;
            } else if (char === ']') {
                // End of current bracket section - return result and current index
                return [result, index + 1];
            } else {
                // Regular character
                result += char;
                index++;
            }
        }

        return [result, index];
    };

    return helper(s, 0)[0];
};

// Time Complexity: O(n)
// Space Complexity: O(n)

/**
 * @param {string} s
 * @return {string}
 */
var decodeString = function(s) {
    const stack = [];
    let currentStr = '';
    let currentNum = 0;

    for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) {
        const char = s[i];

        if (char >= '0' && char <= '9') {
            currentNum = currentNum * 10 + parseInt(char);
        } else if (char === '[') {
            // Push current state to stack
            stack.push([currentStr, currentNum]);
            currentStr = '';
            currentNum = 0;
        } else if (char === ']') {
            // Pop from stack and decode
            const [prevStr, num] = stack.pop();
            currentStr = prevStr + currentStr.repeat(num);
        } else {
            // Regular character
            currentStr += char;
        }
    }

    return currentStr;
};
```

透過第二個 stack 倒轉第一個 in-stack 的順序，以達到 FIFO 的效果
```
// Time Complexity: O(1) for push, pop, peek, empty;
// Space Complexity: O(n)

class MyQueue {
    constructor() {
        this.inStack = [];
        this.outStack = [];
    }

    /** 
     * @param {number} x
     * @return {void}
     */
    push(x) {
        this.inStack.push(x);
    }

    /**
     * @return {number}
     */
    pop() {
        if (!this.outStack.length) {
            this.pushToOutStack();
        }

        return this.outStack.pop();
    }

    /**
     * @return {number}
     */
    peek() {
        if (!this.outStack.length) {
            this.pushToOutStack();
        }

        return this.outStack[this.outStack.length - 1];
    }

    /**
     * @return {boolean}
     */
    empty() {
        return this.peek() === undefined;
    }

    pushToOutStack() {
        while (this.inStack.length) {
            this.outStack.push(this.inStack.pop());
        }
    }
}
```

