层序遍历，使用队列。每遍历一层，深度+1，直到遍历到最下面一层

```java
class Solution {
    public int maxDepth(TreeNode root) {
        if(root == null) return 0;
        Queue<TreeNode> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        queue.add(root);
        int depth = 0;
        while(!queue.isEmpty())
        {
            int size = queue.size();
            for(int i = 0;i < size;i++){
                TreeNode node = queue.poll();
                if(node.left != null) queue.add(node.left);
                if(node.right != null) queue.add(node.right);
            }
            depth++;
        }

        return depth;
    }
}
```
时间复杂度O(N) N为二叉树节点个数

先判断当前两个节点是否相同，如果不同，直接返回false。如果相同无法得出最终结论，需要递归进入下一层继续判断子树
```java
class Solution {
    public boolean isSameTree(TreeNode p, TreeNode q) {
        if(p == null && q != null) return false;
        if(p != null && q == null) return false;
        if(p == null && q == null) return true;
        if(p.val != q.val) return false;

        boolean l = isSameTree(p.left,q.left);
        boolean r = isSameTree(p.right,q.right);

        return l && r;
    }
}
```
时间复杂度O(N) N为树的节点数量

回溯维护一个List，当递归到叶子节点时，List中保存的数字就是一路从root到当前根节点的所有数字。使用StringBbuilder拼接所有数字，即是当前路径表示的数字

```java
class Solution {
    List<Integer> path = new ArrayList<>();
    int res = 0;
    public int sumNumbers(TreeNode root) {
        path.add(root.val);
        recursion(root);
        return res;
    }

    public void recursion(TreeNode root){
        if(root.left == null && root.right == null){
            StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
            for(int num : path){
                sb.append(num);
            }
            res += Integer.parseInt(sb.toString());
            return;
        }

        if(root.left != null){
            path.add(root.left.val);
            recursion(root.left);
            path.remove(path.size() - 1);
        }

        if(root.right != null){
            path.add(root.right.val);
            recursion(root.right);
            path.remove(path.size() - 1);
        }
    }
}
```
时间复杂度O(N)

层序遍历，记录每一层的最左侧的值，不断覆盖变量，最终记录的是最深一层的最左侧的值
```java
class Solution {
    public int findBottomLeftValue(TreeNode root) {
        Queue<TreeNode> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        queue.add(root);
        int res = 0;
        while(!queue.isEmpty())
        {
            int size = queue.size();
            for(int i = 0;i < size;i++){
                TreeNode node = queue.poll();
                if(i == 0){
                    res = node.val;
                }
                if(node.left != null) queue.add(node.left);
                if(node.right != null) queue.add(node.right);
            }
        }

        return res;
    }
}
```
时间复杂度O(N)

序列化时：前序遍历记录每个节点用逗号分开，空节点记为#
反序列化：将序列化结果以逗号分开，存储进队列，用队列递归构造树
```java
public class Codec {
    StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
    int count = 1;

    public String serialize(TreeNode root) {
        if(root == null){
            sb.append("#").append(",");
            return sb.toString();
        }

        sb.append(root.val).append(",");
        serialize(root.left);
        serialize(root.right);
        return sb.toString();
    }

    public TreeNode deserialize(String data) {
        Queue<String> queue = new LinkedList<>();
        String[] pre = data.split(",");
        for(String s : pre){
            queue.offer(s);
        }
        return build(queue);
    }

    public TreeNode build(Queue<String> queue){
        if(queue.isEmpty()) return null;
        String rootStringVal = queue.poll();
        if(rootStringVal.equals("#")) return null;
        int rootVal = Integer.parseInt(rootStringVal);

        TreeNode root = new TreeNode(rootVal);
        root.left = build(queue);
        root.right = build(queue);

        return root;
    }
}
```

