**【Day 16】513. 找树左下角的值**

**思路**

从右往左层序遍历,最后一个节点就是左下角的点

```python
class Solution:
    def findBottomLeftValue(self, root: Optional[TreeNode]) -> int:
        q = deque([root])
        while q:
            node = q.popleft()
            if node.right: q.append(node.right)
            if node.left: q.append(node.left)
        return node.val
```

